{"data":[{"name":"106:1","price":"1. குறைஷிகளுக்கு (பிரயாணத்தின் மீது) விருப்பமுண்டாக்கி,","arabic":"لِإِيلَٰفِ قُرَيۡشٍ","category":["106 (Quraish)","Quraish","Surah Quraish"],"ayahNumber":6194,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"liīlāfi qurayshin ","translations":["For (the) familiarity","(of the) Quraish","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["liīlāfi","qurayshin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,4575]]}},{"name":"106:2","price":"2. குளிர்கால பயணத்தையும், கோடைகால பயணத்தையும் அவர்கள் விரும்பிக் கைகொள்ளும்படி செய்ததற்காக,","arabic":"إِۦلَٰفِهِمۡ رِحۡلَةَ ٱلشِّتَآءِ وَٱلصَّيۡفِ","category":["106 (Quraish)","Quraish","Surah Quraish"],"ayahNumber":6195,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"īlāfihim riḥ'lata al-shitāi wal-ṣayfi ","translations":["Their familiarity","(with the) journey","(of) winter","and summer","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["īlāfihim","riḥ'lata","al-shitāi","wal-ṣayfi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1510],[2,1510,2290],[3,2290,4960],[4,4960,8795]]}},{"name":"106:3","price":"3. (அதற்கு நன்றி செலுத்துவதற்காக) இவ்வீட்டின் இறைவனையே அவர்கள் வணங்கவும்.","arabic":"فَلۡيَعۡبُدُواْ رَبَّ هَٰذَا ٱلۡبَيۡتِ","category":["106 (Quraish)","Quraish","Surah Quraish"],"ayahNumber":6196,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"falyaʿbudū rabba hādhā al-bayti ","translations":["So let them worship","(the) Lord","(of) this","House","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["falyaʿbudū","rabba","hādhā","al-bayti",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1550],[2,1550,2160],[3,2160,2770],[4,2770,5525]]}},{"name":"106:4","price":"4. அவன்தான் (அவர்கள் உழவடித்துப் பயிரிடாமலே இந்த வர்த்தக பிரயாணத்தின் மூலம்) அவர்களுடைய பசிக்கு உணவளித்து வருகிறான். (கொலை, களவு முதலிய கொடிய) பயத்திலிருந்தும் அவர்களுக்கு அபயமளித்தான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَطۡعَمَهُم مِّن جُوعٖ وَءَامَنَهُم مِّنۡ خَوۡفِۭ","category":["106 (Quraish)","Quraish","Surah Quraish"],"ayahNumber":6197,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transli